    "MissionTokens": {
        "Contractor|RecoverItemTitle": [
            "Bleeding Edge Tech",
            "Turning the Tables",
            "Upgrade Grab"
        ],
        "Contractor|RecoverItemDescription": [
            "Managed to hunt down a rare piece of tech only for it to get snagged by someone right at the last second. Tracking it isn't exactly hard, but I'd rather not keeping chasing this thing.\n\nHead to <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> and get it back for us. The people over there probably don't even know what it is, so let's do them a favor and take it off their hands. No idea if it's being guarded, so up to you how you wanna deal with any potential threats.\n\nOnce you've got it, take it to <EM4>[Destination|Target|Address]</EM4> and then we'll send over the creds.\n\n-Bit Zeros",
            "If you're looking to make some primo creds then we've got a job for you. Someone stole a piece of tech from one of our transporters and is trying to sell it back to us.\n\nThe nullbrain didn't even realize we were tracing their comms when they comm'd us up trying to extort us. Now all you have to do is go to <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>, grab the tech, and take it to <EM4>[Destination|Target|Address]</EM4>. We don't know what the situation is over there so maybe bring a weapon or two with you. Could be fine though.\n\n-Bit Zeros",
            "We need someone to head over <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> and find a piece of tech for us. You don't need to know what the tech is/who it belongs to/why we need it, all you have to do is take it to <EM4>[Destination|Target|Address]</EM4> and we'll get you paid. There could be people protecting it, but that's kind of your problem.\n\n-Bit Zeros"
        ],
        "Location|Address": [
            "Central Core & Power",
            "Sector 1",
            "Service Entrance",
            "Storage Depot",
            "Sector 2"
        ],
        "Destination|Target|Address": [
